    {
      "id": "b9c566ad-b69c-4cce-b4af-9bf9573abc52",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use a 2-stage system with data collected from the first year of a program to predict whether the students will be successful or not. In this context, success is defined in 2 terms:",
