    {
      "id": "f13ec598-b9df-45f9-83cc-c677d80b347e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "More than developing a predictive model and testing it on data collected throughout 12 years, the authors also propose a segmentation of students. Results show that the RF model is effective at predicting success AND that the segmentation may be useful in the development of optimal strategies to promote high achievement and mitigate student failure. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "f13ec598-b9df-45f9-83cc-c677d80b347e",
        "parent": {
